race.comment: FLYING CELICA (7) has really hit form over the mile including a last start win here. Not much tougher and has a win and a placing from two tries here at the trip. Expected to go close again. REGGIE'S FOLLY (4) has been going well winning two of the last four, including an all the way win last time at Ipswich. Expected to give a sight. DON'T DISS AROUND (3) has placed four of last five and looks well placed to break through. Placed only try course and distance and suited this grade. SON OF BEEBEE (6) was close-up in a similar race last time. Finds it hard to win but can feature on recent form. SAVVY BEE (9) was always back and wide latest but worth another chance off a low draw.
